      • isEmpty

        org.apache.flink.api.java.DataSet<Boolean> isEmpty()
        Returns a 1-element dataset containing a boolean value which indicates if the collection is empty. A collection is considered empty, if it contains no logical graphs.
        Returns:
        1-element dataset containing true, if the collection is empty or false if not
